{"tid":191437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港大學「獅龍共舞－華藉英軍史」(2017年4月7日至5月27日)","createTime":"2017-04-08T01:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T04:44:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98b71cd4da4995e8af7d714a274d7b8a0620012a","tid":191437,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"FROM Watershed Hong Kong:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/WatershedHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FWatershedHK&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=0fac442e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/WatershedHK</a><br />\n<br />\nThe British Chinese Armed Forces Heritage Project: &quot;Chinese Dragons, British Lions&quot; Exhibition &amp; Thematic Talks<br />\n「獅龍共舞－華藉英軍史」展覽及主題講座<br />\n<br />\n日期：2017年4月7日至5月27日<br />\n地點：香港大學百周年校園賽馬會教學大樓7樓702創意空間MC3<br />\n<br />\n過去一個半世紀，華人以不同身份效力於英軍，廣為人知的有華勇營、華工團、日後的皇家香港軍團和香港軍事服務團等。今次展覽有資料版介紹口述歷史受訪者、部隊轉變和影響，並有電視及電腦播供大家回顧這些故事。欲知更多？立即自己去睇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/kzw6m9b3h/17760180_434587466876027_3150143391359140753_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2Fkzw6m9b3h%2F17760180_434587466876027_3150143391359140753_n.jpg&h=d1fb67a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/eapkd5iw3/17630055_434587730209334_2745527143036182109_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Feapkd5iw3%2F17630055_434587730209334_2745527143036182109_n.jpg&h=5578a0f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e3b6a4852ba470c4969651d2f66ba25130aa901","tid":191437,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T01:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/kz8qzu1p5/17759974_434587696876004_3974557318879388528_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fkz8qzu1p5%2F17759974_434587696876004_3974